abstract: The Senate capped a difficult seven months by approving financing for the F.D.A. and expanding access to experimental treatments for people with terminal illnesses.
snippet: The Senate capped a difficult seven months by approving financing for the F.D.A. and expanding access to experimental treatments for people with terminal illnesses.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON â€” The Senate on Thursday gave final approval to legislation to finance the Food and Drug Administration, clearing the measure for President Trump and tapping drug manufacturers once again to help pay for the federal review of prescription drugs and medical devices.

abstract: The British publicist has a moment in the media glare as the broker of the 2016 meeting between Donald Trump Jr. and a Moscow insider.
snippet: The British publicist has a moment in the media glare as the broker of the 2016 meeting between Donald Trump Jr. and a Moscow insider.
lead_paragraph: A new peripheral character in the Trump universe stepped into the spotlight this week: the entertainment publicist and former tabloid reporter Rob Goldstone.
